{"tid":594371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我老豆係個無名英雄","createTime":"2018-03-15T19:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T19:30:04.000Z","uid":56738,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4902bb3df6240a4d0323646382331190d2fea76e","tid":594371,"uid":56738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:04:02.000Z","msg":"佢唔係消防員 唔係做咩偉大職業 只係一個貨車佬<br />\n<br />\n佢一個人養起一頭家 雖然有時好麻媽 但個膊頭比全世界人都橫<br />\n<br />\n佢差d破產 30幾40歲人重頭開始 而加比到個舒適既環境我地<br />\n<br />\n佢對過老母唔住 用左幾年時間補償 而加同老母日日都好撚sweet<br />\n<br />\n我老豆同大家個老豆都差唔多<br />\n<br />\n但如果你真係愛佢 試下分享下你既日常比佢知 等老豆可以了解你<br />\n<br />\n一句老豆埋黎攬下唔使曬你1秒鐘 但就可以同老豆拉近一大折<br />\n<br />\n愛放係心入面得你自己知 表達埋出黎就雙方都知<br />\n<br />\n老豆我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84496fbc1999830faf545f612574520fcd8fa993","tid":594371,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:04:37.000Z","msg":"收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37aea926b8ab84fbe277348c7613b6200b924869","tid":594371,"uid":52984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:06:20.000Z","msg":"乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c4fd6de2eb83483ebb27b3df8965a6321af2ed","tid":594371,"uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:17:42.000Z","msg":"我老豆反而做人無行過差踏過錯"},{"pid":"ea4227e72ceedcd9c1fa0cf18f0dfd5c17780ad8","tid":594371,"uid":37329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:30:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}